  m_text: "The I piece can also rotate down into the ground.\n\nThis is where it
    gets tricky: \n\nIf the overhang is on the left, simply tuck the piece under
    and rotate cw.\n\nIf the overhang is on the right, you must right rotate it twice,
    then tuck and rotate ccw."
